{
  "stem": "6052.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But [BACKGROUND NOISE] one outstanding matter was that when we came to Turkey, or when we left Turkey, that we were given a lot of food into our train.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Jewish congregation sent us all kinds of food from all kinds of factories.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What was more than ample supply was cheeses-- hard cheeses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we as children, in a joking way, threw out the 'ballast,' we called it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's a ballast because we felt we could not eat so many cheeses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were hundreds of cheeses, large cheeses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had other foods also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we threw it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what is memorable-- it-- it sounds funny today, but it was memorable still.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We threw out the cheeses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we said, why should we throw it out just yet when we pass stations where-- where soldiers are stationed, we-- we'll throw it out there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we really-- there were many soldiers stationed, and we threw it out there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Until some high-authority officer came to our-- our train and said, this you cannot do it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You should not do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You should not do such thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we were understanding it that we should not do it, and we did not continue.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we arrived safely from there into-- from Turkey, we arrived safety into Aleppo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The entire--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, this was a car pick-up, which was-- not-- it was a hour or two hours.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember how long it exactly took.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember very well that we very-- we were very crowded in that car which picked-- picked us up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Praying was very much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you see, we followed-- we were still-- I was very much traditional, you see?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I insisted on praying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I insisted on praying.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
